{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4285507d03","title":"关于干部问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"03101c39d5","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"4285507d03","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"59cda4a865","type":"title","text":"关于干部问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"4285507d03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ea686d343","type":"paragraph","text":"我们这些干部都是经过长期锻炼的，还是要有人站出来，现在的情况是站出来就打。我们的事情是要人挂帅的，红卫兵能挂帅吗？今天上台，明天就可能被打倒，原因是他们政治上不成熟。现在我们要做很多工作，使那些主要干部站出来，哪怕是黎元洪式的，出来两年也行。红卫兵不行，没有经过锻炼，这样的大事情，信不过他们。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"4285507d03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7920b85d2c","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"4285507d03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f726ce5c9","type":"paragraph","text":"要爱护干部，要支持革命领导干部出来，革命小将现在叫他们挂帅还不行，有个培养的过程，但小将是可爱的，是无产阶级革命事业的接班人。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"4285507d03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"735aafc274","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"4285507d03","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b8c0b32558","type":"paragraph","text":"全国应该有更多的第一把手站出来。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"4285507d03","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":605,"end":605}}}},"__N_SSG":true}